{"tid":2108334,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"本土派料推李家偉戰區一 對決泛民任啟邦","createTime":"2020-07-14T12:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T21:19:01.000Z","uid":246044,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4f0217076187c5285aa12d08514586e1ec9a7375","tid":2108334,"uid":246044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"本土派在各區初選均取得不俗成績，新界西的結果更明顯佔優。而功能組別中的區議會（第一），預料將成為本土派和傳統泛民之間的角力。<span class=\"red\">本土派的屯門區議員李家偉，獲不少本土派支持去馬</span>，如無意外將對決大埔區議員，新民主同盟的任啟邦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hSjFESz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhSjFESz.jpg&h=ac3e15b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豉油: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dbchannel.hk/photos/a.122771689139239/281839849899088/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdbchannel.hk%2Fphotos%2Fa.122771689139239%2F281839849899088%2F&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuDMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=305270b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dbchannel.hk/photos/a.122771689139239/281839849899088/</a>"},{"pid":"4377f94b56d3c185dfa1c9cb257a2afe45d164ed","tid":2108334,"uid":246044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:52:02.000Z","msg":"支持本土"},{"pid":"d9bcd4e112aa32035f164c2a1d58ced093425c0b","tid":2108334,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:53:36.000Z","msg":"唔該傾掂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b959d532a308bc073cafcc7c0c8ff3413a2f95f","tid":2108334,"uid":246044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed4344ab9893ba42e0d9b11e79427ceecd008eb","tid":2108334